Description: # SimpleBlockchainDatabase [![Open Source Helpers](https://www.codetriage.com/demg-dev/simpleblockchaindatabase/badges/users.svg)](https://www.codetriage.com/demg-dev/simpleblockchaindatabase)
        In this repository you can found a simple Database based on blockchain technology.
        
        > **IN THIS MOMENT THE DATABASE JUST WORK AS LOCALLY AND ONE DEVICE**
        
        ## Version
        **1.1.2**
        
        ## LICENSE
        [MIT License](LICENSE)
        
        ## Requirements
        Python >= 3.6
        
